(Love Sets Sail with the Warship,
Collective Wedding Ceremony)

19
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,970
Left turn! Right turn!

20
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,320
Chief.

21
00:03:39,570 --> 00:03:40,630
The newlyweds are ready.

22
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:41,560
Awaiting your command.

23
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,880
Proceed as planned.

24
00:03:42,900 --> 00:03:43,600
Yes, Sir!

25
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:59,100
(Love Sets Sail with the Warship,
Collective Wedding Ceremony)

26
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:06,350
♪Rain falls into the sea,
let the North Star♪

27
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:11,750
♪Guide you back with answers,
at the edge of dreams♪

28
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:13,760
Zong Qing.

29
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:14,480
Here!

30
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,730
Explain the flag signals to the brides.

31
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:17,490
Yes, Sir!

32
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,400
The sea is our witness.

33
00:04:20,400 --> 00:04:21,880
The warship is our matchmaker.

34
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:23,200
Together for life.

35
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,370
Loyal to the end.

36
00:04:27,490 --> 00:04:29,730
Please welcome our officiant,
Brigadier Wang Lang.

37
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:33,000
♪Occupy my mind♪

38
00:04:33,930 --> 00:04:35,200
Liang Xuguang, Zhou Dan.

39
00:04:35,370 --> 00:04:35,880
Here!

40
00:04:35,930 --> 00:04:36,490
Step forward.

41
00:04:36,490 --> 00:04:37,130
Yes, Sir!

42
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,760
Staff Sergeant Liang Xuguang.

43
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,880
Ten years of service.

44
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,490
Recipient of one second-class merit

45
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:46,730
and two third-class merits.

46
00:04:46,915 --> 00:04:49,200
Twice awarded
for outstanding service in the brigade.

47
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:52,130
To carry out
overseas peacekeeping missions,

48
00:04:52,570 --> 00:04:54,280
you and your partner, Zhou Dan,

49
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:56,810
have postponed your wedding
three times in two years.

50
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,570
Liang Xuguang.

51
00:04:58,930 --> 00:04:59,810
Zhou Dan.

52
00:05:00,730 --> 00:05:03,690
Thank you both for your dedication
to the country and the people.

53
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:05,250
This wedding

54
00:05:05,490 --> 00:05:08,730
is a gift from the entire brigade
to you.

55
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,730
Thank you,
Brigadier and our fellow comrades.

56
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:16,170
Soldiers are born
to be on the battlefield.

57
00:05:16,170 --> 00:05:19,010
I'm proud
to be part of the Marine Corps,

58
00:05:19,050 --> 00:05:21,280
and I'm proud
to be in a dual-military family.

59
00:05:24,570 --> 00:05:25,280
Fall back in line.

60
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:26,250
Yes, Sir!

61
00:05:26,490 --> 00:05:28,910
♪It's your eyes♪

62
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:29,730
Peng Tiechao.

63
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:30,440
Here!

64
00:05:30,810 --> 00:05:31,440
Step forward.

65
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,010
Yes, Sir!

66
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,170
Sergeant Peng Tiechao.

67
00:05:35,693 --> 00:05:37,440
College graduate,
enlisted for eight years.

68
00:05:37,730 --> 00:05:39,570
Repeatedly served aboard the Peace Ark.

69
00:05:39,570 --> 00:05:41,760
Traveled thousands of miles
delivering medical aid.

70
00:05:42,170 --> 00:05:43,520
Always on the front lines.

71
00:05:43,730 --> 00:05:44,880
Devoted your youth.

72
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,570
When you were enlisted,

73
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,730
you were just a teenager.

74
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:52,130
Now, you're a fully qualified sailor.

75
00:05:52,930 --> 00:05:55,490
Congratulations to you
and your partner, Xu Jing.

76
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:59,690
Your campus romance
has blossomed in the military.

77
00:05:59,782 --> 00:06:01,960
No regrets for our youth.
We're part of a strong force.

78
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:04,490
I swear to dedicate my life
to the military.

79
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:07,810
Fall in.

80
00:06:07,810 --> 00:06:08,490
Yes, sir!

81
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,050
Miss Ning Juan.

82
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:12,730
Would you step forward too?

83
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,130
Miss Ning Juan

84
00:06:15,537 --> 00:06:18,400
has been in a long-term relationship
with Master Sergeant Wang Yongjun.

85
00:06:18,690 --> 00:06:20,200
They've loved each other for years.

86
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,490
As a university lecturer,

87
00:06:22,490 --> 00:06:23,880
while nurturing students,

88
00:06:24,050 --> 00:06:26,810
she also cared
for Youngjun's parents like her own.

89
00:06:27,050 --> 00:06:29,370
She's gone through hardships
we can hardly imagine.

90
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,810
Miss Ning Juan,

91
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:32,200
thank you.

92
00:06:32,404 --> 00:06:34,050
Thank you for everything you've done.

93
00:06:34,337 --> 00:06:37,170
I'd like to say thank you
to the unit leaders for the great honor.

94
00:06:37,490 --> 00:06:38,320
From today on,

95
00:06:38,337 --> 00:06:39,490
besides being an educator,

96
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,730
I have another title I'm proud of,

97
00:06:41,730 --> 00:06:42,640
military spouse.

98
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:50,980
♪You're the one, the longing, the flame♪

99
00:06:51,093 --> 00:06:52,893
Let's welcome Deputy Commander Lan.

100
00:06:52,915 --> 00:06:56,620
♪The choice I'll never regret♪

101
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:57,840
Comrades.

102
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:01,930
I feel truly happy that we're holding

103
00:07:02,782 --> 00:07:04,050
this collective wedding today.

104
00:07:04,490 --> 00:07:05,640
And I'm grateful too.

105
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:09,640
I'm grateful
to these brilliant young women

106
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:12,200
for marrying our soldiers

107
00:07:12,382 --> 00:07:13,610
and becoming military spouses.

108
00:07:14,400 --> 00:07:16,960
Among them is my own daughter,

109
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,170
Yangyang.

110
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,490
You didn't join the military.

111
00:07:20,730 --> 00:07:21,930
As your father, I regret that.

112
00:07:22,730 --> 00:07:24,490
But you chose to be a military spouse.

113
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:28,170
In another way, that's a choice
to be part of the military.

114
00:07:28,930 --> 00:07:30,690
And I'm proud of you.

115
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,250
Thank you, Yangyang.

116
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,810
Thank you, fellow military spouses.

117
00:07:36,250 --> 00:07:37,490
A soldier must

118
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:40,640
protect the country, the nation,

119
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,490
and the people.

120
00:07:42,810 --> 00:07:44,730
To fight or go to war

121
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:47,400
means facing danger and sacrifice.

122
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:51,250
Like every profession,

123
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:54,050
that is his responsibility.

124
00:07:55,010 --> 00:07:57,960
But for a military spouse,

125
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,810
choosing to build a life with a soldier

126
00:08:01,010 --> 00:08:03,250
takes tremendous courage.

127
00:08:04,730 --> 00:08:07,570
Not only are you military spouses,

128
00:08:08,010 --> 00:08:10,930
but you must also support our soldiers
from behind the scenes.

129
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:14,050
With your hard work,

130
00:08:14,570 --> 00:08:17,200
the home front is secure.

131
00:08:18,010 --> 00:08:19,370
With your sacrifice,

132
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,810
our soldiers' resolve is stronger.

133
00:08:22,490 --> 00:08:24,570
With your care,

134
00:08:24,570 --> 00:08:27,440
their lives are richer.

135
00:08:28,730 --> 00:08:32,210
Your husbands
are the Great Wall of our nation.

136
00:08:32,210 --> 00:08:36,130
And you are the strong support
behind that wall.

137
00:08:37,730 --> 00:08:41,490
Please accept the salute of a veteran.

138
00:08:42,450 --> 00:08:43,490
Salute!

139
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:05,520
No, don't give it to me.

140
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,850
Xin, just take it.

141
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:07,970
I really don't want it.

142
00:09:07,970 --> 00:09:09,520
I saved it especially for you.

143
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:11,130
I don't want to get married so soon.

144
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:12,400
You have to take my lucky bouquet.

145
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,400
Give it to someone else.

146
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:15,880
Xin.

147
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,160
Mr. Wang.

148
00:09:17,450 --> 00:09:18,680
Just take it.

149
00:09:19,210 --> 00:09:21,400
Today, you're not just a reporter.

150
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,450
You're also Yangyang's bridesmaid.

151
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:27,880
Alright, then.

152
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:33,010
If you need anything else
for this interview,

153
00:09:33,330 --> 00:09:34,520
just let Wu Si know.

154
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:36,250
Where is he?

155
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:38,400
How would I know?

156
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:40,250
He's over there.

157
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,730
Go find him.

158
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:43,450
I'll pass.

159
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,560
If Wu Si's father

160
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,850
could see all this today,
he'd be so proud.

161
00:10:08,450 --> 00:10:09,760
Oh my.

162
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:13,400
How was the wedding?

163
00:10:13,730 --> 00:10:14,970
Be patient.

164
00:10:15,010 --> 00:10:15,970
Let me open it.

165
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:17,880
Here's the video.

166
00:10:18,370 --> 00:10:20,250
You actually caught the bouquet.

167
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:21,680
How amazing!

168
00:10:21,680 --> 00:10:23,680
I didn't have to catch it, Mom.

169
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,730
Lan Yangyang insisted
on giving it to me.

170
00:10:25,730 --> 00:10:28,137
As if she wanted to let everyone know
that I'm not married yet.

171
00:10:28,450 --> 00:10:30,210
Then prove them wrong.

172
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:32,090
Shut their mouths for good.

173
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:35,680
Dad, you should've seen

174
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:37,400
how heartbroken Mr. Lan was today.

175
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,610
You would change your mind

176
00:10:38,610 --> 00:10:40,400
about marrying me off so soon.

177
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,160
Of course, he was heartbroken.

178
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:47,040
What Dad wouldn't be,
seeing his daughter

179
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:50,330
get married?

180
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:54,610
Listen here.

181
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:56,210
You'd better get married soon.

182
00:10:57,490 --> 00:10:58,850
Seriously, look at this...

183
00:11:00,010 --> 00:11:01,090
We're all parents.

184
00:11:01,090 --> 00:11:03,090
His daughter is already married,

185
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,090
but mine is still single.

186
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:06,730
There, there.

187
00:11:06,730 --> 00:11:08,250
I'll get married eventually.

188
00:11:08,490 --> 00:11:10,250
Well, I so envy him.

189
00:11:10,250 --> 00:11:11,040
Come on.

190
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:12,400
No rush. That day will come.

191
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,330
It'll happen.

192
00:11:52,370 --> 00:11:53,210
Hurry! Move!

193
